{
  "stem": "22582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they established like an auxiliary that-- so my sister got me, somehow, a stamp that I could work like this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and that was the-- right after that was-- they started to get the-- the whole town-- they-- they came out with the announcement that everybody-- everybody had to go.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had a list who had to come back, who come, who had to go and-- downstairs at certain time and certain day and to be in front of the house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and they are going to be sent out to a work camp somewhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody thought that that is what it's, of course, going to be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody had to-- to take-- they told you what you-- what you had to take with you, you know, the blanket, and this and that, like to go to work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To-- and that was in-- and they took those people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they-- most of them shot quite a few thousand outside of town-- outside of town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the rest they send out somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody heard of them anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite a few thousand were shot because it was-- and Tarnow was the place, I think, that-- I-- I don't-- they said it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some [INAUDIBLE] somewhere, that-- that's where people were shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's where it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the-- the main thing is most people who were-- who were not shot, they were shipped out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nobody heard about anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If somebody would know, you wouldn't go down with blankets and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it was the first-- the first time that we heard about that somebody-- that it was organized killing.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
